run_analysis.R Codebook
July 26th, 2015
Codebook prepared by steveqk

Variable: subject
Description: subject identifier
Datatype: numeric

Variable: activity
Description: Type of activity generating the observation (WALKING, WALKING_UPSTAIRS, WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS, SITTING, STANDING, LAYING)
Datatype: text

Variable: feature
Description: features of units used by subjects during activities
Datatype: text

Variable: measure_function
Description: function (std or mean) of observation used to calculate reported mean
Datatype: text

Variable: direction
Description: axial signals in X, Y, Z directions
Datatype: text

Variable: observation_mean
Description: mean of the std or mean observations by subject by activity by feature by measure_function by direction
Datatype: numeric
